title: Post the most /facepalm thing you heard in solo q
body:
I'll start this Nasus Tps in the other teams base while me and the team are playing D because they had supers up and it goes like this 

"Nasus TPs in base, trys to solo a full hp turret while getting attacked by super minions and a heim" 

"OMFG why are you guys pushing up without any wards?"
